9 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
10 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 11 O.S. 2021, Section 43-103, is
11 amended to read as follows:
12 Section 43-103. A. Municipal regulations as to buildings,
13 structures, and land shall be made in accordance with a
14 comprehensive plan and be designed to accomplish any of the
15 following objectives:
16 1. To lessen congestion in the streets;
17 2. To secure safety from fire, panic, and other dangers;
18 3. To promote health and the general welfare, including the
19 peace and quality of life of the district;
20 4. To provide adequate light and air;
21 5. To prevent the overcrowding of land;
22 6. To promote historical preservation;
23 7. To avoid undue concentration of population; or
